<item>
            <title>[LU-12082] Interop: conf-sanity test 82a fails with &#8216;stripe is already set on /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2, /usr/bin/lfs setstripe -o 45964,57544,708 /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2 should fail&#8217;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12082</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity test_82a fails for b2_10 client and 2.7.22.2 servers with the following seen in the client test_log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt; 
/usr/bin/lfs setstripe -o 45964,57544,708 /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-1

/usr/bin/lfs setstripe -o 45964,57544,708 /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2

/usr/bin/lfs setstripe -o 45964,57544,708 /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2
 conf-sanity test_82a: @@@@@@ FAIL: stripe is already set on /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2, /usr/bin/lfs setstripe -o 45964,57544,708 /mnt/lustre/d82a.conf-sanity/f82a.conf-sanity-2 should fail 
  Trace dump:
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:5337:error()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/conf-sanity.sh:5868:test_82a()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;This test started failing in inerop testing with 2.7.x servers before December 2017; this is as far back as I&#8217;ve looked for this failure. All failures are 2.11.0, 2.10.x clients with 2.7.x servers. I don&#8217;t see this failure with 2.12 nor master probably because we don&#8217;t interop test these releases with 2.7.x. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at several of these failure for b2_10 client and 2.7.x servers at there are no errors in any of the dmesg nor console logs for any nodes.   &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are several failures for a variety of different Lustre versions:&lt;br/&gt;
2.8.2.10 clients and 2.7.3 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/128ceb24-5bc5-11e8-b9d3-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/128ceb24-5bc5-11e8-b9d3-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
2.10.57.44 client and 2.7.3 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ef08d1d4-0301-11e8-a10a-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ef08d1d4-0301-11e8-a10a-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2.10.57.57 client and 2.7.3 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/672273f2-072e-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/672273f2-072e-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2.10.3 RC1 client and 2.7.19.10 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d96d1db0-f665-11e7-94c7-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d96d1db0-f665-11e7-94c7-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2.10.5 RC1 client and 2.7.19.10 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bd0cc40-98f7-11e8-87f3-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6bd0cc40-98f7-11e8-87f3-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
2.10.7 RC1 client and 2.7.22.2 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f617094e-4303-11e9-9646-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f617094e-4303-11e9-9646-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2.11.0 client and 2.7.3 servers&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c1a4f3de-389a-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c1a4f3de-389a-11e8-960d-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
